"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"寫篇文仲雞過中學生<br />\n<br />\nTvb新聞部好似中大人最多喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e6540047d3c61636f6878b44c180027e2ed65d2","tid":1691984,"uid":30040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"睇呢D冇用㗎，琴晚cctvb直播直頭話成班蒙面人打灰色衫男人，不停打， 其他人傷，點解會俾人打，佢直播果時提都冇提。"},{"pid":"e2b6d66c649d6d18f9e6525c40e8ded44be3f0b4","tid":1691984,"uid":62600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T02:48:26.000Z","msg":"成件事好清楚啦，拉記者都唔拉刀手，唔<span style=\"color: red;\">千企唔好</span>鶳佢點得，佢無事出番來<span style=\"color: red;\">千企唔好</span>再鶳佢，我地唔可以還手架俾人斬都，犯法架"},{"pid":"b2db5328d9b29ae6148287f81e7e9cd401f4da2a","tid":1691984,"uid":19287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T04:03:22.000Z","msg":"Tvb條片del左？"}]}